posting_body: ['REF# 11R121', '$7500 · Brickell · 2/2 · Unfurnished · 1152 Sqft · 801 Sma Residences Condo', 'Call ➟ Text ➟ WhatsApp', "📲 786'*'5O5'*'4314", 'Carlos Manchego', 'Goldstein Realty', 'show contact info', 'Luxury living awaits you at the SLS LUX.', 'This 2 bed 2 bath unit is located on a high floor in one of the most desirable buildings in the area.', 'This building has fantastic amenities including an Outdoor Sky-lounge, rooftop pool, and services designed to indulge its residents.', 'This unit has electric blackout shades in all the rooms, Subzero and Wolf Appliances, and a large wraparound balcony.', 'Pamper yourself at the Ciel Spa and enjoy a full-service fitness center with rock-climbing walls, and a combined tennis and basketball court.', 'Walk across the street to Brickell City Centre and many restaurants/ bars that Brickell has to offer.', '1 assigned space included plus valet for your guest.', 'AS PER BUILDING ADMINISTRATION, SHOWINGS ONLY M/F - 9AM/5PM Condo Association approval required.', 'Read Less', 'REF# 11R121', 'tags:', 'wynwood lofts, paramount miami worldcenter, courvoisier courts, brickell vista, icon brickell, mayfield condo, four ambassadors, south 27 lofts, four seasons residences, wynwood lofts, the mark on brickell, paramount miami worldcenter, direct bay view, two tequesta point, mybrickell, abitare, cite condo, courvoisier courts, brickells flagler homes, quantum on the bay, bay house, courtyards of the grove, three tequesta point, axis on brickell, baltus house, le parc at brickell, the axis on brickell, 1010 brickell, havana lofts condo, three tequesta point, met 1, centro lofts,, grove towers, the plaza at brickell', '_mr11']
